Example of a local installation:

Order matter!!! First install sphinxbase, then pocketsphinx.

Make sure your local folder is already in place, otherwise you won't have anything installed.

1)
sphinxbase:

./autogen.sh --prefix=$(pwd)/../.debug/usr/local/
./configure --prefix=$(pwd)/../.debug/usr/local/
make
make install


2)
pocketsphinx:

./autogen.sh --prefix=$(pwd)/../.debug/usr/local/
(dont need this one -> //./configure --prefix=$(pwd)/../.debug/usr/local/)
make
make install
